---
title: Articles
layout: base
---

{% for post in collections.posts %}
<article class="excerpt">
  <h2><a href="{{ post.url }}">{{ post.data.title }}</a></h2>
  <p><strong>{{ post.data.postdate | formatDate | safe }}</strong></p>
  <p>{{ post.data.description }}</p>
</article>
{% endfor %}

<article id="articles">
  <h2>Featured Articles</h2>
  <p class="lead">You can find me as a writer on <a href="https://www.smashingmagazine.com/author/stephanie-eckles/">Smashing Magazine</a>, <a href="https://css-tricks.com/author/stephanieeckles/">CSS-Tricks</a>, <a href="https://moderncss.dev/">ModernCSS</a>, <a href="https://11ty.rocks/">11ty Rocks</a>, and <a href="https://dev.to/5t3ph">DEV</a>.  Here is a selection of tutorials and articles I'm most proud of, and that have also received appreciation from the wider community.</p>
  <ul role="list" class="scroll-grid container">
    {% for item in writing %}
    <li>
      <div class="sidebar">
        <h3><a href="{{ item.url }}">{{ item.title }}</a></h3>
        <img src="/img/logo-{{ item.source }}.png" alt="" />
      </div>
      {{ item.description | markdown | safe }}
      {% for link in item.links %}
      <a href="{{ link.url }}">{{ link.text }}</a>
      {% endfor %}
    </li>
    {% endfor %}
  </ul>
</article>